            "notes": "The deck focuses on ramping up mana quickly and efficiently to play big threats and overwhelm the opponent with aggressive plays. It utilizes cards like Exploration, Lotus Cobra, and Primeval Titan to accelerate mana production and get ahead of the curve. Cards like Green Sun's Zenith and Worldly Tutor help find key creatures like Emrakul, the Promised End for a powerful finisher. With a mix of land-based ramp spells, creatures, and utility lands, the deck aims to establish a dominant board presence early on and keep up the pressure throughout the game. Lumra, Bellow of the Woods serves as the commander to further enhance the deck's aggro strategy with its abilities and provide additional support for the overall game plan."
